SmartMax Flower Set
With these sets you can create a variety of beautiful flowers! The flower petals are magnetic and so you can create multi-layered flowers.

**Features:**
* Includes two sets: Flower Fun and Flower Power
* Allows kids to experience both the wonders of magnetism and the fascinating world of construction in a safe way
* Each set includes flower-making accessory pieces of varying sizes and colors
* For ages 3 and up

